{"tid":2370115,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭家純侄兒鄭明傑懷疑涉及可疑交易    遭北京燃氣藍天停職","createTime":"2021-01-17T18:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T03:06:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7978962c31c4995304bd91fe9ca28549754dca37","tid":2370115,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T18:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.AijDcxTDDxBf2._vEyAfA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/n1VmmVs2OdykuEW454unmA--~B/aD01ODU7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/a4be365789f98745255079e9e42fb855\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.AijDcxTDDxBf2._vEyAfA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fn1VmmVs2OdykuEW454unmA--~B%2FaD01ODU7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fa4be365789f98745255079e9e42fb855&h=4924d840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北京燃氣藍天(06828)公布，公司發現了若干可疑交易及若干或許存在問題的集團資產。由於董事會現懷疑非執行董事及董事會副主席鄭明傑(鄭家純侄兒)與該事件有關，因此為減輕公司股東及公眾的疑慮，董事會已議決自1月16日起暫停其作為公司非執行董事及董事會副主席的職務，直至另行通知為止。公司正聘用專業團隊，協助搜集有關資料及深入調查該事件，將盡快刊發詳細公告，以向股東及潛在投資者提供進一步消息。<br />\n<br />\n鄭明傑原為北燃藍天聯席主席及行政總裁，去年7月因健康理由，以及投入更多時間發展其他事業，而調任為非執行董事及副主席。"},{"pid":"31f661c88cd66e1ccfc102401b5a4cd80daeae39","tid":2370115,"uid":321374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T02:39:35.000Z","msg":"打土豪，分田地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c5d691371d8ac0e970ac391f870f7114d1a181","tid":2370115,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T02:44:36.000Z","msg":"唔緊要，香港係逃犯天堂黎，做完衰野搵管教棍就一定冇事"},{"pid":"cf1095380cf59554d5ad514194bda5a55c772a0e","tid":2370115,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T02:48:33.000Z","msg":"以為係嗰個鄭家純同佢個侄有可疑交易<br />\n仲等我除定褲入黎"},{"